        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Tanner</ENAMEX>'s stages. The association between <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">glucose</ENAMEX> and lipid
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">profiles</ENAMEX> and the distribution of adipose tissue was also
