          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">puberty</ENAMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">BMI</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">girls</ENAMEX> also increases with stage of sexual
          maturation, but relative fatness is variable, especially
